{{Documentation subpage}}
<!-- Please place categories where indicated at the bottom of this page and interwikis at Wikidata (see [[Wikipedia:Wikidata]]) -->
== Usage ==
:{{Tlc|User Wiktionary}}

If no parameter is supplied, the current page name will be the target.

You can also use:
:{{Tlc|User Wiktionary|Username}}

=== Placement ===

This template may be floated to the right by use of {{para|float|right}}. The default and usually recommended position is to the left.

== Example ==
{| class="wikitable"
! Code
! Result
|-
| {{tlc|User Wiktionary}}
| {{User Wiktionary}}
|-
| {{tlc|User Wiktionary|Username}}
| {{User Wiktionary|Username}}
|}

== See also ==
* {{tl|User Wiktionary 2}}
